{"tid":1596854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貼連儂牆嘅入嚟】929 全球反極權遊行「人鏈」 Poster","createTime":"2019-09-26T16:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T14:27:52.000Z","uid":46891,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4bef534fae79a2737934d4348414160861e97778","tid":1596854,"uid":46891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"今次反極權遊行，全球有咁多城市撐香港，一定唔可以晒在個咁好嘅機會宣傳。Poster 嘅設計係有齊參與城市嘅遊行資料，而posters 黐埋一齊就會變成「人鏈」，象徵全球聯手反極權。各區幫手貼連儂牆嘅巴絲，麻煩幫手將啲posters遍地開花咁周圍黐，特登整黑白方便大家瘋狂咁印。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我要每區同海外都見到「人鏈」 Poster！！！</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n構思圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hsm6V7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhsm6V7Y.jpg&h=2f156acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實物<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p04kf7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp04kf7Y.jpg&h=00b2c774&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nGoogle Drive Download<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1UD259pW6lNK1Eh-EgMn21AqXG8Yy0D1w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1UD259pW6lNK1Eh-EgMn21AqXG8Yy0D1w&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=8b2bae32\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1UD259pW6lNK1Eh-EgMn21AqXG8Yy0D1w</a>"},{"pid":"32e372bae9a8a2897a17f599c847aec466d9183e","tid":1596854,"uid":46891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd812db278677f5adc0febeadcb7bede2cc9aeb1","tid":1596854,"uid":46891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0b559dd5587957bcb8880c338407baadb6901dfb","tid":1596854,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0805f8144bdacd8dbf28b9d7e5b7d85d0774be05","tid":1596854,"uid":164517,"like":0